ns.\n- ConsumerRebalanceMetricsManager.java: Concrete metrics manager for consumer rebalance events, tracking rebalance latency, duration, rates, and failure counts.\n- ShareRebalanceMetricsManager.java: Metrics manager for share consumer rebalance events, extending RebalanceMetricsManager for share-specific metrics.\n\nThese components collectively implement the consumer group rebalance coordination protocol, handling listener callbacks, event propagation, and performance metrics throughout the rebalance lifecycle."
